{"article_id":"FEE84m0TaZmQPYtp","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The no-wall deal","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"that ended the government shutdown","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"was a bitter pill for voters","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"who sent President Trump to the White House ,","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"but they say","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"they ' re still backing him","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"as the border security fight with Democrats enters Round Two .","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"Even as conservative pundits blasted the president for \" caving \" to House Speaker Nancy Pelosi ,","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"voters","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"contacted by The","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"said","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"they aren ' t holding the setback against Mr. Trump .","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"\" I haven ' t lost any confidence in him or faith in him , \"","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"said Brian McKenna , 73 , a retired police officer in Stuart , Florida .","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"\" I ' m dumbfounded","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"that people in this country don ' t see the problem down at the border .","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"The whole issue is about somebody breaking the law","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"and the Democrats defending it . \"","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"While Mr. Trump ' s base still wants a wall or barrier on the U.S.-Mexico border ,","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"their support for the shutdown had slowly eroded","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"as the impasse dragged on for 35 days .","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"\" He lost on this ,","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"but his hands were kind of tied , \"","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"said Gus Lester , 66 , a disappointed Trump supporter on Maryland ' s rural Eastern Shore","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"who said","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"has not yet given up on the president or his border wall .","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"Mr. Lester , a lifelong Democrat and longtime Carpenters Union president","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"who crossed party lines","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"to vote for Mr. Trump in 2016 ,","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"said","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"the government shutdown had to end .","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"\" We still need the wall , \"","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"\" Let ' s see what happens","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"[ three weeks ] from now . \"","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"The president ' s agreement with Democrats calls for House-Senate negotiations on funding for the Department of Homeland Security and border security , with a deadline of Feb. 15 .","depth":5},{"id":36,"text":"Mr. Trump has warned","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"that he could declare a national emergency","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"if he doesn ' t get some amount of money for 230 miles of barriers along the southern border .","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"Said Mr. McKenna ,","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"\" Three weeks from now he ' s going to have do something","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"if [ Democrats ] won ' t negotiate . \"","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"The president weathered harsh criticism from conservative pundits and media personalities","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"for failing to secure funding for a wall .","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"Fox Business host Lou Dobbs , usually a supporter of Mr. Trump , said of the agreement","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"to end the shutdown ,","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"\" Illegal immigrants are surely pleased at the prospect","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"they may soon jump to the front of the line","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"while legal immigrants aren ' t even part of the discussion in the nation ' s capital . \"","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"Conservative activist Ann Coulter called Mr. Trump a \" wimp \"","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"and lamented ,","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"\" It ' s crazy that I expect a president to keep the promise","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"he made every day for 18 months . \"","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"A senior White House official said dismissively of Ms. Coulter ,","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"\" The president of the United States isn ' t going to react to what somebody is screaming on Twitter . \"","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"The official said","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"that Mr. Trump has succeeded in \" elevating border security in the conversation , \"","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"and that negotiations over the next three weeks will target at least 30 House Democrats","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"serving in districts","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"that Mr. Trump won in 2016 ,","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"including 22 freshman lawmakers .","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"\" Nancy","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"[ Pelosi ]","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"has been totally hijacked by the left wing , \"","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"the senior official said .","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"\" He","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"[ Mr. Trump ]","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"hears from Democrats .","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"They know","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"their leadership isn ' t representing their districts . \"","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"Given those dynamics ,","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"the senior official said","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"the president ' s approach will be , \" OK , government ' s open .","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"Let ' s talk . \"","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"A letter","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"written by first-term Rep. Elaine Luria , Virginia Democrat ,","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"and signed by more than 30 House Democrats","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"last week called for a vote on the president ' s border-security proposal","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"after government reopened .","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"White House deputy press secretary Hogan Gidley said","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"\" the dam was beginning to break on the Democrat side","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"and we could get something accomplished .","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"That ' s why the president decided to open the government . \"","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"But others noted","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"that six GOP senators had voted last week for the Democrats ' plan","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"to reopen government","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"without wall funding ,","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"and that Mr. Trump ended the shutdown","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"shortly after a shortage of air-traffic controllers Friday delayed hundreds of flights at several major airports .","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"Republican strategist Ford O ' Connell said","depth":6},{"id":90,"text":"Mr. Trump ' s support will remain intact","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"as long as he keeps fighting for a border wall ,","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"whether in negotiations with Congress or in a court battle over a national emergency declaration .","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"\" He might be taking a short-term hit with his base","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"but really you have to withhold judgment until Feb. 15 , \"","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"\" As long as Trump is seen as committed to border security and physical barriers at the southern border ,","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"it is not going to hurt him in the grand scheme of things . \"","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"The deal ,","depth":7},{"id":99,"text":"while chalked up as a win for Mrs. Pelosi ,","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"puts the burden on Democrats","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"offer a border-security plan .","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"\" Democrats say over-and-over","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"they care about border security at the U.S. southern border .","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"Now we are going to find out just how serious they are , \"","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"Mr. O ' Connell said .","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"\" Trump is making a good faith offer","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"and trying to govern through the legislative process ,","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"and","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"if Congress doesn ' t pick up the ball","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"I wouldn ' t be surprised to see him declare a national emergency . \"","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"Tea Party Patriots founder Jenny Beth Martin ,","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"who met with the president and other conservative leaders at the White House last week ,","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"said","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"the president ' s base is blaming Mrs. Pelosi","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"for refusing to negotiate on border security .","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"\" The whole point of this exercise is to secure the border , \"","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"she said on Fox & Friends .","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"\" What President Trump has promised , she ' s not willing to negotiate on . \"","depth":8},{"id":119,"text":"She said","depth":8},{"id":120,"text":"Mr. Trump ' s supporters are standing with him","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"in spite of his earlier offer of protections for nearly 1 million illegal immigrants and people with Temporary Protected Status .","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"\" He ' s been willing to go further","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"than some people may even want him to do","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"who are his supporters , \"","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"Ms. Martin said .","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"\" But they understand .","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"They ' re trying to give him the leeway","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"to negotiate .","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"She","depth":12},{"id":130,"text":"[ Mrs. Pelosi ]","depth":12},{"id":131,"text":"hasn ' t been willing to do that at all . \"","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"Hispanic faith leaders","depth":5},{"id":133,"text":"who met with Mr. Trump at the White House Friday","depth":6},{"id":134,"text":"just after the shutdown ended","depth":6},{"id":135,"text":"told him","depth":4},{"id":136,"text":"they support his efforts on border security .","depth":3},{"id":137,"text":"\" You ' ve done a very good job","depth":5},{"id":138,"text":"being the leader","depth":6},{"id":139,"text":"we need you to be , \"","depth":6},{"id":140,"text":"Pastor Ramiro Pena of Christ the King Baptist Church in Waco , Texas , told the president .","depth":4},{"id":141,"text":"\" We want to say","depth":5},{"id":142,"text":"thank you for doing everything","depth":7},{"id":143,"text":"you can get aid in a humanitarian way for this crisis","depth":8},{"id":144,"text":"where we need it most ,","depth":8},{"id":145,"text":"securing our borders ,","depth":7},{"id":146,"text":"and providing for law enforcement and the Border Patrol everything","depth":8},{"id":147,"text":"they need .","depth":8},{"id":148,"text":"He added ,","depth":5},{"id":149,"text":"\" One thing","depth":9},{"id":150,"text":"you have not done , Mr. President ,","depth":9},{"id":151,"text":"is manufacture a humanitarian crisis .","depth":8},{"id":152,"text":"It ' s real .","depth":7},{"id":153,"text":"I ' m grateful","depth":7},{"id":154,"text":"that you have shown leadership","depth":8},{"id":155,"text":"to recognize it ,","depth":9},{"id":156,"text":"to call it out ,","depth":10},{"id":157,"text":"and actually do something about it . \"","depth":10}],"relations":[{"parent":315,"left":289,"right":314,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":289,"left":199,"right":288,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":199,"left":175,"right":198,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":175,"left":164,"right":174,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":164,"left":161,"right":163,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":161,"left":159,"right":160,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":159,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":160,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":163,"le